    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome, fighters and spectators!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rixe is about to begin, so fight for glory and entertainment !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defend your base</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rounds are both scripted and randomized to make every run singular, picking and placing enemies from a pool of dozens of learnable pattern enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229870/extras/27e531dd3634d3f3e3d411a93acb0361.poster.avif?t=1771876001\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229870/extras/27e531dd3634d3f3e3d411a93acb0361.webm?t=1771876001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Define your gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Every hero has unique abilities and 8 stackable upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229870/extras/f7cd47e8c3c0d3521ece300ee91fa564.apng?t=1771876001\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229870/extras/f7cd47e8c3c0d3521ece300ee91fa564.poster.avif?t=1771876001\" class=\"bb_img\" width=182 height=184 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play online with friends</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo, with up to 2 friends of yours, or join a lobby online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229870/extras/cfb014045c97643f8691259b09df0a93.poster.avif?t=1771876001\" width=162 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229870/extras/cfb014045c97643f8691259b09df0a93.webm?t=1771876001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take up the challenge</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy, Normal, and Hard modes are available in both solo and co-op play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229870/extras/dbb6d13eccbd0bb2bed54cbb2b38acb0.apng?t=1771876001\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229870/extras/dbb6d13eccbd0bb2bed54cbb2b38acb0.poster.avif?t=1771876001\" class=\"bb_img\" width=170 height=67 /></picture></span></p>",
